{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":834200}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":0,"pos":2}]},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20][chara:200900:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Oh look, that was awesome! Watch!"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It hit that barrel spot-on!"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But can you defeat a Witch with that?"},{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"autoTurnNoDelay":1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFull":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh? Umm, ahahaha..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200900}]},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-8","voiceFullStop":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Probably...not?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Absolutely not."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-10"},{"eyeClose":0,"id":200201,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ugghhh!@Why, oh why, am I even training?!"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm not proud to say it,@but I haven't improved one bit!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I'm more of the advisor type, y'know?@Strategy and background support and@all that?"},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]A PATHETIC Magical Girl,@unfit for physical labor!"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Our powers come from our wishes@as Magical Girls."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So if you're unwilling to fight,@there's no hope for any results."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-16"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I mean, yeah...@That might be true..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But...wishes, huh...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Actually, wait."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What AM I fighting for so desperately...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-20"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]......"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Isn't that obvious?"},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]You're helping me fulfill my wish,@so that you can escape from this loop."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, yeah...that IS true, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200201,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-24"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu, don't let yourself get distracted."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-25"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Just focus on honing your magic."},{"chara":[{"id":200201,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]For now, your goal is to keep training until@you're able to split that barrel in half."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104209/vo_full_910113-010-27"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Whaaa...?@You're so cruel..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
